        "role": "Founder, Wax | Wane Store · The Happiest Hour LLC",
        "bio_text": "I started Wax | Wane because I was tired of spending money on products that did not work and wellness advice that was either too complicated or too expensive to act on. I am not a dermatologist or a scientist — I am someone who did the research so you do not have to, and built a store around only the things I would actually put on my own face and in my own home.",
        "bio_text_2": "Korean skincare changed my skin in a way that years of Western products never did. Crystals gave me a ritual that made self-care feel intentional instead of performative. And once I understood what EMFs actually are, I could not un-know it — so I found products that address it without the fear-mongering. Everything in this store is something I use, trust, and would recommend to my best friend.",
